{"tid":1470324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國政府或派包機接載國民離開香港","createTime":"2019-08-14T04:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T05:11:14.000Z","uid":32577,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"105dbda52fbbbe09a19cdf513cac50b4ec2cc2d4","tid":1470324,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:55:48.000Z","msg":"香港國際機場連續兩日未能正常運作，泰國政府計劃派出兩架飛機，協助滯留香港的國民撤離。<br />\n<br />\n泰國傳媒引述泰國皇家空軍發言人說，準備了一架C130運輸機及一架A340空中巴士，到香港接載國民回國，相關官員亦隨時候命。空軍已制定撤僑計劃，但未知飛機能否降落香港機場。<br />\n<br />\n曼谷郵報引述空軍總司令說，已經要求官員密切注視情況。總理巴育表示，泰國駐港總領事館正定期評估情況，呼籲身處香港的所有泰國人避開示威活動地區，政府亦促請國民延遲非急切需要的行程。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474561-20190814.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474561-20190814.htm&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6w%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=f062d36d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474561-20190814.htm&h=3b3a591e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474561-20190814.htm</a>"},{"pid":"120ece058ff741808f07733f36748fe17ff920d6","tid":1470324,"uid":212003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:02:38.000Z","msg":"撤僑咁撚大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe90a10ae5e88780a5a2bb96ff3e1e50312e5c7","tid":1470324,"uid":174120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:03:28.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"99df2cc539647044912d91b2e4833e3f4d4cc1e2","tid":1470324,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:05:14.000Z","msg":"點解唔飛深圳 明知有人塞機場仲飛香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e21966b4fc7ed9f60646c9585457221cf4ef72","tid":1470324,"uid":21035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99df2cc539647044912d91b2e4833e3f4d4cc1e2","tid":1470324,"uid":58630,"like":